Problem Statement

Our company lacks a modern e-commerce presence, forcing customers to place orders via phone or email, which creates friction in the buying process and limits our sales potential. Manual order processing requires 2-3 hours daily for order entry, inventory checks, and payment coordination. This antiquated system results in abandoned sales due to inconvenient ordering processes, delayed order fulfillment, inventory discrepancies, and inability to capture impulse purchases. Additionally, we have no visibility into customer shopping behavior, cart abandonment rates, or conversion analytics that could inform marketing strategies.

Functional Requirements

Product catalog with categories, images, and detailed descriptions. Shopping cart with add/remove/quantity updates and persistent sessions. Secure checkout process with guest and registered user options. Payment processing with credit card and PayPal integration. Order management system with status tracking and email confirmations. Inventory management with stock level tracking and out-of-stock handling. Customer account creation with order history and profile management.

Required Languages

Python (Django/Flask), JavaScript (React/Vue.js), HTML/CSS